Package org.itemscript.core.gwt

Class Summary
GwtConfig A JsonConfig implementation for the GWT environment that gives access to connectors for HTTP, cookies, and javascript.
GwtCookieConnector A connector class that allows you to store values in browser cookies.
GwtHttpConnector A connector for retrieving JSON values via HTTP.
GwtJavaScriptConnector A connector class that allows you to access values in JavaScript objects defined in the host page.
GwtJsonCreator A JsonFactory for the GWT environment.
GwtJsonParser Parses the string representation of a JSON object into a set of JsonValue-derived objects.
GwtJsonpConnector A connector for retrieving values via JSONP in GWT.
GwtSystem An EntryPoint class for GWT that creates a static JsonSystem instance.
MinimalGwtConfig A minimal JsonConfig implementation for the GWT environment.
MultipleGet A class to help with asychronously loading multiple resources.
MultipleGetCallback Subclass this to supply a callback to MultipleGet.
RequestUtils This class assists in the creation and use of GWT Requests.
